{"tid":1467292,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我哋應該冷靜落嚟反省下，諗下跟住點做","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:11:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:31:57.000Z","uid":210102,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cecc97e3fdfa40d847b818d3f4c2e3953aa88a65","tid":1467292,"uid":210102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:11:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 不割席！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我哋應該要自我反省今次行動有啲乜嘢唔完美嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n下次緊記<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好畀仇恨沖昏頭腦</span><br />\n<br />\n如果唔係就會畀對家拎嚟做新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想提多次大家民意好緊要， 大部分出嚟遊行嘅市民都係<span style=\"color: gold;\">淺黃</span><br />\n<br />\n 我哋唔可以連佢哋都失去埋， 如果唔係<span style=\"color: green;\">大遊行罷工</span>嗰啲唔會再有咁多人和應！<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申： 第一次開post，sorry for 1999"},{"pid":"10190280fec49c25ec244dce4f34ffe738b63357","tid":1467292,"uid":210102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:10.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"a386eac8e01dcfa016f6ee9bfa29e5a220289904","tid":1467292,"uid":210102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:13.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"3307c36de649e5b6eee2c8992ea4c4e05dae5a6a","tid":1467292,"uid":67553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de0edb4e33e874ba4fe916eaa0a94eb63e28d029","tid":1467292,"uid":210102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:44.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"98ab2e1efbb66375a8fe51b40818254e6a060093","tid":1467292,"uid":210102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:20:32.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"ed08971be7815a06758f54ac0fb9f582861889f7","tid":1467292,"uid":210102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r